  "steps": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "Search the north-east bookcase in the Seers' Village church.",
        "es": "Busca en la estantería del noreste en la iglesia de Seers' Village."
      },
      "chatOptions": [
        "Accept"
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "Read the ragged book.",
        "es": "Lee el libro andrajoso."
      },
      "chatOptions": [],
      "highlightTerms": [
        "ragged book"
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "Use soft clay on the book to get the key mould. If you do not have soft clay, you can mine some from the clay rocks in the western mine of the workshop then use it on the sink in the northern room.",
        "es": "Usa arcilla blanda en el libro para obtener el molde de la llave. Si no tienes arcilla blanda, puedes extraerla de las rocas de arcilla en la mina occidental del workshop y luego usarla en el fregadero de la sala norte."
      },
      "chatOptions": [],
      "highlightTerms": [
        "soft clay",
        "key mould",
        "clay rocks"
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "Enter the Elemental Workshop and go into the mine to the west. Mine 3 elemental rocks, killing the earth elementals that appear, then pick up the 3 elemental ores that they drop. Simply killing the earth elementals wandering around the mine will not yield the ore.",
        "es": "Entra en el Elemental Workshop y dirígete a la mina del oeste. Extrae 3 rocas elementales, matando a los earth elementals que aparezcan, y luego recoge los 3 minerales elementales que sueltan. Simplemente matar a los earth elementals que deambulan por la mina no dará mineral."
      },
      "chatOptions": [],
      "highlightTerms": [
        "Elemental Workshop",
        "elemental rock",
        "earth elemental",
        "elemental ore"
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "In the fire elemental room (south), use the elemental ore on the furnace to create 3 elemental bars. 4 coal is required per bar.",
        "es": "En la sala del fire elemental (sur), usa el mineral elemental en el horno para crear 3 lingotes elementales. Se necesitan 4 de carbón por lingote."
      },
      "chatOptions": [],
      "highlightTerms": [
        "elemental bar"
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "Use 1 elemental bar on the furnace again to make a ragged elemental key.",
        "es": "Usa 1 lingote elemental en el horno de nuevo para hacer una ragged elemental key."
      },
      "chatOptions": [],
      "highlightTerms": [
        "ragged elemental key"
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "Climb down the hatch in the centre of the middle room.",
        "es": "Baja por la trampilla en el centro de la sala del medio."
      },
      "chatOptions": []
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "Prime the remaining two elemental bars (see primed bar on how to do this) using the jig cart, but '''don't''' infuse them with the Mind machine.",
        "es": "Prepara (prime) los dos lingotes elementales restantes (consulta primed bar para saber cómo hacerlo) usando el jig cart, pero '''no''' los infundas con la Mind machine."
      },
      "chatOptions": [],
      "highlightTerms": [
        "primed bar"
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "Go down the northwest stairwell.",
        "es": "Baja por la escalera noroeste."
      },
      "chatOptions": []
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Starting out",
      "text": {
        "en": "In the middle of the hallway, open the 'Body door' on the western wall with the ragged elemental key.",
        "es": "En el medio del pasillo, abre la 'Body door' en la pared oeste con la ragged elemental key."
      },
      "chatOptions": []
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "isImage": true,
      "section": "The puzzle",
      "filename": "Elemental Workshop III Map.png",
      "caption": "The control layout",
      "image": "https://runescape.wiki/images/Elemental_Workshop_III_Map.png?f13db"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "The puzzle",
      "text": {
        "en": "Head down the stairs.",
        "es": "Baja las escaleras."
      },
      "chatOptions": []
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "The puzzle",
      "text": {
        "en": "Label the levers as follows and use the interface to move them. The levers on the north and south are the same, and the levers east and west are the same so feel free to use the closest lever to your current orientation. You can use the Minigame window to hit the levers, you don't need to run to each one.",
        "es": "Etiqueta las palancas de la siguiente manera y usa la interfaz para moverlas. Las palancas del norte y del sur son iguales, y las del este y oeste son iguales, así que puedes usar la palanca más cercana a tu orientación actual. Puedes usar la ventana del minijuego para accionar las palancas, no necesitas correr hasta cada una."
      },
      "chatOptions": []
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "The puzzle",
      "text": {
        "en": "The \"Reset\" and \"Undo\" levers can be found on the west wall (when the camera is not locked into the fixed overhead view; otherwise, they're to the north)",
        "es": "Las palancas de \"Reset\" y \"Undo\" se encuentran en la pared oeste (cuando la cámara no está fijada en la vista cenital; en caso contrario, están al norte)"
      },
      "chatOptions": []
    },
